						               													<description>La d&amp;eacute;tanque is a game of p&amp;eacute;tanque, dice and square balls at the same time!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It's the same principle as p&amp;eacute;tanque, you throw the cochod&amp;eacute; (the jack dice) and then each team tries to position their dice as close as possible to the cochod&amp;eacute;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Where d&amp;eacute;tanque brings an additional playful aspect is that one side of each of the dice represents a super power. Swap the place of a dice, multiply the points by two or divide them ... We are not at the end of our surprises!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Added to this are the different sides of the cochod&amp;eacute; which can make you play a whole game on one foot, throwing with 2 hands or throwing with your left hand if you are right-handed and vice versa ... A lot of fun!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first team to reach 30 points win&amp;#10;&amp;#10;La d&amp;eacute;tanque mini weighs about 700 g with 43mm diameter dice and easier to carry around or play inside.&amp;#10;La d&amp;eacute;tanque weighs about 3.5 kg with 75mm diameter dice and let you play outside&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
